{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Define anti-Christian hostility & issue guidance for schools, police & business",
        "additional_details": "On 9 March 2026 the Government adopted a definition and tsar for anti-Muslim hostility as part of the \u201cProtecting What Matters\u201d plan. We believe Christians deserve a definition such as this, as in our view many Christian children face bullying in schools and Christian-principled businesses face boycotts and harassment. We ask for Christians to have a definition as that for Muslims, and we hope that creating this in England can encourage consistency across the UK.",
        "background": "Define \u201canti-Christian hostility\u201d mirroring the 2026 anti-Muslim hostility definition and appoint a tsar to oversee it effectiveness. Mandate school guidance on bullying, require police to record incidents as anti-Christian hostility hate incidents, and issue guidance for Christian businesses. ",
